✨ Key Features
    Automated Scriptwriting: Uses the @n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chainLlm node with Google Gemini to draft conversational, 2-minute scripts from any topic input.
    Professional Voice Synthesis: Integrates with the Murf AI API (specifically the en-US-Abigail voice) to create high-fidelity, human-like narration.
    Automated File Retrieval: Includes a Podcast Downloader node that automatically fetches the final audio file from the Murf API response.
    Chat-Triggered Workflow: Designed to be triggered via a chat interface, making it accessible for non-technical users to generate content on the fly.

🛠️ Workflow Architecture
     Trigger: Chat message received via n8n Chat Trigger.
     Logic: The Podcast Script Generator (Gemini) processes the input into a friendly, label-free plain text script.
     Synthesis: The script is POSTed to the Murf AI /v1/speech/generate endpoint.
     Download: An HTTP Request node captures the resulting audioFile URL and downloads the binary data.

🚀 Getting Started
    Prerequisites
      An n8n instance (v1.x or higher).
      Google Gemini (PaLM) API Credentials.
      A Murf AI API Key.
📋 Use Cases
       Daily News Briefs: Convert RSS feeds or headlines into quick daily updates.
       Educational Content: Turn lesson summaries into "listen-while-you-learn" audio.
       Social Media Marketing: Generate high-quality voiceovers for short-form video content (TikTok/Reels).
